  <div class="node__content">
    
            <div property="schema:text">
<p>Echo School District understands that the COVID-19 virus and subsequent school closures in our state are difficult for students, families and staff. We know this situation has disrupted learning for thousands of students.</p>
<p>In the event that students are able to access resources, we are providing the following information and links.</p>
<p>We will update this page with new resources when available.</p>
<p><a class="file file--mime-application-pdf file--application-pdf" data-entity-type="file" data-entity-uuid="47e1a302-b1ef-47f4-90a4-669ad8542d38" href="/sites/echo.k12.or.us/files/inline-files/MCSD%20Online%20Learning%20Resources%202.pdf" rel="nofollow">Learning Resources</a> (PDF)</p>
<p><a href="https://echo.k12.or.us/teachers-pages" rel="nofollow">Teacher Pages</a> -- to see specific resources from your own classroom teacher, visit and choose your teacher's name.</p>
<p> </p>
